---
/**
 * Redesigned Benefits Section
 */
---

<section class="benefits section-pad">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="benefits-header reveal">
            <h2>Vedic Meditation gives you life back.</h2>
            <div class="accent-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>Learn to relax and settle your nervous system.</p>
                <p class="outcome">Feel less pressure, more calm.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>
                    Release accumulated stress chemistry and restore healthy
                    function of your body and mind.
                </p>
                <p class="outcome">Return to balance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>Experience deep rest that restores energy and clarity.</p>
                <p class="outcome">
                    Reduce fatigue and think clearly and creatively.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>Create time in your day that is entirely yours.</p>
                <p class="outcome">Space and time for yourself.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>Balance your emotions and maintain a sense of ease.</p>
                <p class="outcome">
                    A positive influence on yourself and others.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>
                    Build a stable inner foundation to respond to life's
                    demands.
                </p>
                <p class="outcome">Interact with composure.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>Live life aligned with nature's intelligence.</p>
                <p class="outcome">Feel whole and like yourself again.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item reveal">
                <p>Establish yourself in Being.</p>
                <p class="outcome">
                    Evolve, expand your happiness and actually enjoy life.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .benefits {
        background: var(--color-indigo);
        color: var(--color-warm-white);
    }
    .benefits-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 80px;
    }
    .benefits-header h2 {
        font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px);
        color: var(--color-warm-white);
        font-style: italic;
    }
    .benefits-header .accent-line {
        background: var(--color-eucalyptus);
    }
    .benefits-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 48px 80px;
    }
    .benefit-item {
        padding-left: 24px;
        border-left: 1px solid var(--color-sea-green);
    }
    .benefit-item p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: rgba(244, 242, 238, 0.8);
        line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .benefit-item .outcome {
        color: var(--color-golden-seed);
        font-style: italic;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .benefits-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
